headline: Fiserv acquires tech consulting firm
summary: The deal for Smith Consulting Group is designed to give Fiserv’s bank and credit union customers deeper technical expertise.

headline: Fiserv (FI): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Fiserv has gotten torched over the last six months - since March 2025, its stock price has dropped 41.8% to $128.99 per share. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
